<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ログイン | 慶應教科書フリマ (Keio Book Loop)</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@300;400;500;700;900&family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        keio: {
                            blue: '#002F6C',
                            red: '#9E0B0E',
                            gold: '#C5A059',
                            dark: '#0B132B'
                        }
                    },
                    fontFamily: {
                        sans: ['Noto Sans JP', 'sans-serif'],
                        serif: ['Noto Serif JP', 'serif'],
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
    <style>
        .keio-stripe {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #002F6C 42%, #9E0B0E 42%, #9E0B0E 58%, #002F6C 58%);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 font-sans min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-between">

    <!-- Top Tricolor Stripe -->
    <div class="keio-stripe h-1.5 w-full"></div>

    <div class="flex-grow flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-12">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-slate-100 max-w-md w-full overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-2xl">
            
            <!-- Keio Brand Header Section -->
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-50 to-white px-8 pt-8 pb-4 text-center border-b border-slate-100">
                <!-- Styled Crossed Pens Emblem -->
                <div class="relative inline-block mb-3">
                    <div class="absolute -inset-1 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-keio-blue to-keio-red opacity-10 blur"></div>
                    <div class="relative w-16 h-16 bg-white rounded-full border border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm">
                        <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-keio-blue" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                            <path d="M4 20L10 14M20 4L14 10" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                            <path d="M10 14L13 11L11 9L8 12L7 15L10 14Z" fill="currentColor" class="text-keio-red" opacity="0.8"/>
                            <path d="M14 10L11 13L13 15L16 12L17 9L14 10Z" fill="currentColor" class="text-keio-blue" opacity="0.8"/>
                            <path d="M4 20C4 20 5 17 7 15" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                            <path d="M20 4C20 4 17 5 15 7" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <h1 class="font-serif text-2xl font-extrabold text-keio-blue tracking-wider mb-1">
                    慶應教科書フリマ
                </h1>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 font-medium uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">
                    Keio Book Loop
                </p>
                <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 bg-amber-50 rounded-full border border-amber-200">
                    <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber-500 animate-pulse"></span>
                    <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-amber-800">keio.jp 専用認証</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Login Form -->
            <div class="p-8">
                <form action="/login" method="post" class="space-y-5">
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-xs font-bold text-slate-700 mb-1.5 uppercase tracking-wider">
                            メールアドレス (@keio.jp)
                        </label>
                        <div class="relative">
                            <input 
                                type="email" 
                                name="email" 
                                placeholder="example@keio.jp" 
                                required
                                class="w-full pl-4 pr-4 py-3 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-keio-blue focus:bg-white transition-all text-sm text-slate-800 placeholder-slate-400 font-medium"
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-1.5">
                            <label class="block text-xs font-bold text-slate-700 uppercase tracking-wider">
                                パスワード
                            </label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="relative">
                            <input 
                                type="password" 
                                name="password" 
                                placeholder="••••••••" 
                                required
                                class="w-full pl-4 pr-4 py-3 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-keio-blue focus:bg-white transition-all text-sm text-slate-800 placeholder-slate-400"
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <button 
                        type="submit"
                        class="w-full bg-keio-blue hover:bg-slate-900 text-white font-bold py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl shadow-lg shadow-blue-900/10 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-blue-900/20 active:scale-[0.98] transition-all text-sm tracking-widest mt-2"
                    >
                        ログイン
                    </button>
                </form>

                <div class="mt-8 text-center border-t border-slate-100 pt-6">
                    <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mb-2">
                        アカウントをお持ちではありませんか？
                    </p>
                    <a 
                        href="/signup" 
                        class="text-xs font-extrabold text-keio-red hover:text-red-700 transition-colors inline-flex items-center gap-1"
                    >
                        新規塾生登録を行う
                        <svg class="w-3C h-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/>
                        </svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- elegant professional footer -->
    <footer class="py-6 text-center text-slate-400 text-[10px] tracking-wider border-t border-slate-100 bg-white">
        &copy; 2026 慶應教科書フリマ (Keio Book Loop) . All Rights Reserved.<br>
        <span class="text-[9px] mt-1 inline-block text-slate-300">「実学の精神」に基づき、塾生同士の知の循環をサポートします。</span>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>